data.name: ArgumentType
data.value: Parametesr's type(s) for completion. Availables: [Flag | FlagOrValue | Required | File | Directory | List]

data.name: Arguments
data.value: Completion candidates for the parameter arguments. Can define completion text and its description, separated by a tab (\t) or newline (\n, \r).

data.name: ArgumentCompleter
data.value: ScriptBlock that returns completion candidates for the parameter arguments.

data.name: VariableName
data.value: Name of this parameter's argument variable.

data.name: Style
data.value: Specify Parameter style. If ommited, inhertes from the parent CommandCompleter's style.

data.name: Error.NotSpecifiedAnyParameterNames
data.value: At least one of 'StarndardName', 'LongName' or 'ShortName' must be specified.
